{
  "id": "5c94f77fb8e3720017e2f130",
  "title": "円周率",
  "created": 1553266565,
  "updated": 1553268181,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c94f77fb8e3720017e2f130",
      "text": "円周率",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266565,
      "updated": 1553266565
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f7faaff09e0000cb3a60",
      "text": "円周率を「3.14...」という並びだと考えて、その並びに美しさや神秘を見出す感覚に共感できない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266682,
      "updated": 1553266731
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f82faff09e0000cb3a61",
      "text": "円の半径を一辺とする正方形の面積に比べて、円の面積は3.14倍。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266735,
      "updated": 1553266770
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f852aff09e0000cb3a62",
      "text": "円の直径に比べて、円周の長さは3.14倍。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266770,
      "updated": 1553266825
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f86eaff09e0000cb3a63",
      "text": "一方、[$ \\pi / 4 = 0.785...] を使うと、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266798,
      "updated": 1553266911
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f8afaff09e0000cb3a64",
      "text": "円に外接する正方形の面積に比べて、円の面積は0.785倍。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266864,
      "updated": 1553266894
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f8e0aff09e0000cb3a66",
      "text": "円に外接する正方形の周の長さに比べて、円周の長さは0.785倍。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266912,
      "updated": 1553266935
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f784aff09e0000cb3a5f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/f3f4340e7ae1c63cbb81b4d8c8ecd575]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266565,
      "updated": 1553266646
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f8ffaff09e0000cb3a68",
      "text": "後者の方が美しいと思う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266944,
      "updated": 1553266983
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f927aff09e0000cb3a69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266983,
      "updated": 1553266983
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f927aff09e0000cb3a6a",
      "text": "そもそも、10進表記は、地球人が10本指の生き物であることに起因するローカルルールに過ぎない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553266983,
      "updated": 1553267065
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f9acaff09e0000cb3a6c",
      "text": "指が16本の知性体は当然10進表記をしないので、円周率を10進表記した数の列は、普遍的ではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553267117,
      "updated": 1553267187
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94f9f4aff09e0000cb3a6f",
      "text": "表記法として一番普遍性の高いのは2進表記である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553267188,
      "updated": 1553267276
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94fa4baff09e0000cb3a70",
      "text": "しかも円周率が2進表記された場合、1/4は2ビットのシフトに過ぎないのでビットの並びは同一になる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553267276,
      "updated": 1553267313
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94fba3aff09e0000cb3a72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553267620,
      "updated": 1553267620
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94fba4aff09e0000cb3a73",
      "text": "なお、円に外接する多角形の面積とその多角形の周の長さは一致する。これは美しい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553267620,
      "updated": 1553267654
    },
    {
      "id": "5c94fdd4aff09e0000e2ea7f",
